      • setUpdateSketchBuilder

        public void setUpdateSketchBuilder(com.yahoo.sketches.theta.UpdateSketchBuilder udBldr,
                                   boolean direct,
                                   boolean rebuild)
        Sets the theta UpdateSketch builder used to create the theta UpdateSketches.
        Parameters:
        udBldr - the theta UpdateSketchBuilder
        direct - true if direct (off heap) mode is desired. Instead of actual off heap memory this will emulate that behavior by using an on-heap byte array accessed by the Memory package. Performance-wise it is the same except for issues of garbage collection, which is not the purpose of this test.
        rebuild - set true if rebuild is desired

      • setTrialsProfile

        public void setTrialsProfile(int lgMinTrials,
                             int lgMaxTrials,
                             int lgMaxU,
                             int ppo)
        This sets the profile for how the number of trials vary with the number of uniques. The number of trials is the maximum until the number of uniques exceeds k, whereby the number of trials starts to decrease in a power-law fashion until the minimum number of trials is reached at the maximum number of uniques to be tested.
        Parameters:
        lgMinTrials - The minimum number of trials in a trial set specified as the exponent of 2. This will occur at the maximum uniques value.
        lgMaxTrials - The maximum number of trials in a trial set specified as the exponent of 2.
        lgMaxU - The maximum number of uniques for this entire test specified as the exponent of 2. The first trail set starts at uniques (u = 1).
        ppo - The number of Points Per Octave along the unique value number line that will be used for generating trial sets. Recommended values are one point per octave to 16 points per octave.
